# how to start react project
- manually (not recommender atleast for the beginners)
- different packages tools.

## create react app
```
npm install -g create-react-app

npx create-react-app <project_name>
npx create-react-app demo1
cd demo1
npm start
```

Error faced
```
npm install ajv --save-dev

```

## set react app
```
npx set-react-app <project_name> 
npx set-react-app demo2
cd demo2
npm start

``` 

## vite
```
npm install vite --save-dev

npm create vite@latest <project_name>
npm create vite@latest demo3
select the framework => React
select a variant => javascript
cd demo3
npm run dev
```

